$interpreted: Tica: The long-anticipated Christmas Tica makes her debut!
Tica: Huh, weird; I remember the villagers told me that there are people living here?
Koll: Grrrrr~!
Tica: No bullying cute little doggie!
Tica: Hmph, those monsters are terrible.
Koll: Arooo...
Tica: No need to be sad, little doggie! This is for you!
Koll: Aro?
Tica: Merry Christmas!
Roger: Kittyeyes, what's the matter? Is there something on my face?
Kittyeyes: I...... I......

Kittyeyes: (I really want to give him the present...
but what if brother Roger doesn't like it...)
Kittyeyes: (Ahh~~ No good no good no good! If I keep dragging it out, Christmas will be over! I have to conjure up the courage!)
Kittyeyes: Brother Roger! I have something for...

Tica: Let's try this again. The long-anticipated Christmas Tica makes her debut! 
Here~ a present for both of you!
Kittyeyes: Who are you!? Why are you giving brother Roger a present? What do you want?
Kittyeyes: (Could it be... that she likes brother Roger as well!?)

Tica: Ooh, you guys are such a cute couple~
Wish both of you a very Merry Christmas~~~
Kittyeyes: (A couple? So to other people, brother Roger and I look like a couple? And a cute one too?)
Roger: What a strange girl. This one is probably for Kittyeyes, right?
Roger: Eh? So you got a present too?
Kittyeyes: This... I plan to give this to brother Roger...

Dagger: That brat... she even gave the dog a present.
Where did she go!?
Dagger: Why do you guys have it too!
Dagger: Apologies. She made a mistake. These are for someone else.
Dagger: Hey! Tica! Stop!

Kittyeyes: That big dumb bear took my present!
That's my present for brother Roger! GIVE IT BACK!!!
Koll: Growwwl!~~
Roger: Why is Koll chasing behind him as well?

Roger: Kittyeyes? Where are you going?
Wait for me!
